  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle Dashboard currently uses `react-scripts` 4.0.0.  As best I can tell, this is responsible for our one remaining critical security alert, which is `immer`.  If we upgrade to 5.0.0, it will use an up-to-date version of `immer` that will get rid of the security alert.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Nevermind, turns out we can't immediately do this; react-scripts 5.0.0 requires Node 14.  So we can't do this while we still support Node 12.  See [release notes](https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app/releases/tag/v5.0.0).\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.5.4",
